{
  "calls": [
    {
      "id": "09070c73-2906-42d7-b89a-06786ffe89f2",
      "to_number": "+919581158927",
      "name": "bhargavi",
      "status": "completed",
      "transcript": "[{\"bot\": \"Hi, is this bhargavi? This is Tanya from Kshema General Insurance. I'm calling to share some quick details about our insurance plans and claims. Is now a good time to talk for two minutes?\", \"message_id\": \"f69bc8df-c60f-436f-9b1c-7e39b90e28ef\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:56:15.739+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Okay.\", \"message_id\": \"554530\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:56:28.348+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"Just to understand-what kind of insurance are you looking for right now? Is it for you, your family, or for a vehicle or business?\", \"message_id\": \"fa1edc51-10ab-4eb1-bc4c-b84401646b57\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:56:29.566+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"How many types of insurance\", \"message_id\": \"557585\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:56:40.983+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"you are providing?\", \"message_id\": \"557867\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:56:42.122+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"Okay, Kshema General Insurance provides a few main types of insurance: - Group Personal Accident Policy: covers accidental death and disability for groups. - Individual Personal Accident Policy: covers accidental death and disability for individuals. - Shop Insurance Policy: protects shops and commercial establishments against fire, burglary, and other risks. - Crop Insurance: covers losses to crops for farmers. Does that make sense? Which one are you interested in for yourself or your family, or for your business?\", \"message_id\": \"9fe0f8f3-b444-44d5-b4c1-b3c3eb3bc342\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:56:45.050+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Okay. Types of crop insurance?\", \"message_id\": \"565766\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:57:24.345+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"Right, Kshema offers crop insurance plans that are comprehensive and customised for small farmers. There are a few types: - Government schemes like Pradhan Mantri Fasal Bima Yojana (PMFBY), which covers food crops, oilseeds, and commercial crops against natural disasters and other risks. - Weather-Based Crop Insurance Scheme (RWBCIS), which compensates for weather-related losses. - Kshema\u2019s own products-Sukriti and Prakriti-tailored to specific crops, regions, and farming needs. These plans can be customised\", \"message_id\": \"2daa4fa2-240e-4744-871b-b105a0b8509e\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:57:26.629+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Okay. You can\", \"message_id\": \"569911\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:57:55.859+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"Got it, bhargavi. Would you like a quick explanation of the coverage and claim steps for crop insurance, or do you want me to share plan details now?\", \"message_id\": \"88ed19ea-5b4c-4f08-b4c3-ba482634b8b5\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:57:56.730+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Blake\", \"message_id\": \"571148\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:58:06.560+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"would you\", \"message_id\": \"571274\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:58:07.378+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"explain the difference between Sukruti and Pakruti?\", \"message_id\": \"571707\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:58:10.225+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"Okay, here\u2019s the difference: Prakriti is a comprehensive crop insurance solution that protects farmers against eight natural perils, covers one-hundred plus crops, and calculates premium based on cultivation cost, crop duration, and location. Sukriti is also a Kshema product for crop insurance, but the exact details or differences compared to Prakriti are not available in my notes right now. If you want, I can arrange a callback with more details about Sukriti. Would you like that, or should I explain the claim steps for Prakriti now?\", \"message_id\": \"75d0cbd1-9c77-4c68-9a53-614d898f3463\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:58:13.220+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Okay. I\", \"message_id\": \"576349\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:58:49.880+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Explain the claims.\", \"message_id\": \"576528\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:58:51.038+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"For Tatati.\", \"message_id\": \"576710\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:58:52.221+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"Here\u2019s how claims work for Prakriti crop insurance: If a covered event like flood, hailstorm, fire, or animal attack happens, the farmer can file a claim with Kshema. The insurer will assess the damage to the crops and settle the claim as per the policy terms. The payout is calculated based on the crop loss and the insured value. Want me to share the step-by-step claim process or any other details?\", \"message_id\": \"0d3d9569-da0f-4afb-9856-bcad96542b87\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:58:55.220+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Okay. But I have another insurance details.\", \"message_id\": \"580694\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:59:25.363+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Like\", \"message_id\": \"580811\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:59:26.124+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"my friend have a fractured leg.\", \"message_id\": \"581172\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:59:28.489+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Is there any policy? Is there for,\", \"message_id\": \"581623\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:59:31.469+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"Right, bhargavi. Yes, Kshema has personal accident policies that cover accidental injuries like fractures. There are two main options: - Group Personal Accident Policy: For groups, covers accidental death and disablement, including fractures. - Individual Personal Accident Policy: For individuals, covers accidental death, permanent and temporary disability, and weekly benefits for temporary total disablement. So, your friend can\", \"message_id\": \"530bb0ad-000e-4420-a592-8061dd545f42\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:59:32.734+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"like, my friend have only\", \"message_id\": \"585840\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T12:00:03.783+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"one month\", \"message_id\": \"586004\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T12:00:04.849+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"rest for the fractured leg.\", \"message_id\": \"586566\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T12:00:08.763+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Is\", \"message_id\": \"586773\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T12:00:10.459+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Samsung the temporary or\", \"message_id\": \"587158\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T12:00:12.986+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"permanent?\", \"message_id\": \"587302\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T12:00:13.919+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"Okay, let me clarify for you, bhargavi. In Kshema\u2019s Individual Personal Accident Policy, there are two types of disability covered: - Temporary Total Disability: This is for injuries like a fractured leg where you need rest and cannot work for a period (for example, one month). The policy offers a weekly benefit payout for this. - Permanent Disability: This is for injuries that cause lasting or lifelong loss of function. So, for your friend\u2019s fractured leg and one-month rest, it falls under temporary total disablement. The policy can provide weekly payouts during the recovery\", \"message_id\": \"1376f363-1eb0-495d-811b-efd317626fdf\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T12:00:15.651+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"pricing\", \"message_id\": \"594024\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T12:00:53.519+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"I don\u2019t have the exact\", \"message_id\": \"18015d22-abfb-4d46-b6df-ca89d522bd76\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T12:00:55.380+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Could you please share the price?\", \"message_id\": \"595590\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T12:00:57.044+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"I don\u2019t have the exact price for the Kshema Individual Personal Accident Policy right now. The premium depends on the plan chosen and coverage options. If you want, I can arrange a callback with the exact pricing details, or share what\u2019s available about the coverage and benefits. What would you prefer, bhargavi?\", \"message_id\": \"382892f4-b813-4212-a2cb-3c77db6dde83\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T12:00:58.961+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Like, would you like\", \"message_id\": \"601342\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T12:01:19.021+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"explain the coverage?\", \"message_id\": \"601734\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T12:01:20.340+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"Sure, bhargavi. The Kshema Individual Personal Accident Policy covers: - Accidental death (full payout) - Permanent total disability - Permanent partial disability - Temporary total disability (weekly benefit for up to one hundred four weeks) You can choose from three plans: Plan A covers death only, Plan B covers death plus permanent disabilities, and Plan C covers death, permanent disabilities, and temporary total disablement. Does that make sense? Want more details on claim steps or anything else?\", \"message_id\": \"15200457-eb9b-4a55-9a22-187d4bf2213e\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T12:01:22.667+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"No. Nothing.\", \"message_id\": \"611261\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T12:01:57.597+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"But, I made\", \"message_id\": \"611772\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T12:01:59.741+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"to know the\", \"message_id\": \"612206\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T12:02:01.524+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"Alright, that\u2019s done from my side. If you want, I can share the key points again quickly later. Bye!\", \"message_id\": \"e4d7e3e4-7cb7-43de-bc3e-8311ac9b9f1f\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T12:02:03.119+00:00\"}]",
