      "name": "bhargavi pennada",
      "status": "completed",
      "transcript": "[{\"bot\": \"Hi, is this bhargavi pennada? This is Tanya from Kshema General Insurance. I'm calling to share some quick details about our insurance plans and claims. Is now a good time for a brief chat?\", \"message_id\": \"2481ac60-7010-444e-b923-cf73f9907afc\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:26:55.101+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Okay.\", \"message_id\": \"358102\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:27:08.917+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"Just to understand-what kind of insurance are you looking for right now? Is it for you, your family, or for a vehicle or business?\", \"message_id\": \"5f2a8c01-368e-4a87-ba38-c78026e90b85\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:27:10.357+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Yes.\", \"message_id\": \"359363\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:27:19.904+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"For business.\", \"message_id\": \"359510\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:27:20.856+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Plans you are\", \"message_id\": \"359765\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:27:22.399+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"providing for business?\", \"message_id\": \"359986\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:27:23.842+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"Okay, for businesses, Kshema offers two main plans: First, there\u2019s the Kshema Shop Insurance Policy. It protects shops and commercial establishments against losses from fire, burglary, and other risks. This plan covers your building, stock-in-trade, equipment, and business contents. It\u2019s designed for small shops, commercial outlets, and service businesses. Second, there\u2019s the Kshema Group Personal Accident Policy. This plan gives financial protection to group members in case of accidental death or disability. It covers permanent and temporary disablement, and there\u2019s a weekly benefit for temporary total disablement. Does that make sense? Would you like more details about coverage or claim steps\", \"message_id\": \"5de9f9fb-390e-4069-bb34-0d9570e99e16\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:27:25.973+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Please.\", \"message_id\": \"365205\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:28:06.335+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"You\", \"message_id\": \"365366\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:28:07.379+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"like, please you tell slowly.\", \"message_id\": \"366471\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:28:10.145+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Too fast, I think.\", \"message_id\": \"367182\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:28:11.964+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"Right, I\u2019ll explain slowly. So, the first plan is Kshema Shop Insurance Policy. It protects your shop or business from losses like fire, burglary, and other risks. You get coverage for your building, stock, equipment, and business contents. The\", \"message_id\": \"08d5e15d-4e8f-4bb9-bd8d-b300035bbaeb\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:28:13.088+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Okay. Fine for that.\", \"message_id\": \"371337\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:28:29.408+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Is there any crop insurance\", \"message_id\": \"371767\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:28:32.223+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"How many types are there?\", \"message_id\": \"372243\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:28:35.741+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"Okay, yes-Kshema does offer crop insurance. There are a few types\", \"message_id\": \"cdc463f4-11cc-4b81-8917-6a49d7350b54\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:28:37.868+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Yeah.\", \"message_id\": \"373343\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:28:41.713+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"So, basically, Kshema\u2019s crop insurance options include: one. Government-backed plans like Pradhan Mantri Fasal Bima Yojana (PMFBY)-these cover notified crops and offer subsidised premiums. two. Weather-based crop insurance schemes-these compensate farmers for losses from unseasonal rain or temperature changes. three. Private plans like Kshema\u2019s own seasonal risk-cover options-these can be customised for specific crops and regions. Would you like to know how the claim process works for crop insurance, or details about coverage?\", \"message_id\": \"4654ffdc-d098-4000-9150-9a1f8ed6ff67\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:28:43.036+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Like,\", \"message_id\": \"377129\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:29:13.448+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Sheema Samriddhi and Sheema Sukriti, they are not\", \"message_id\": \"377840\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:29:18.119+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"I don\u2019t have exact details about \u201cSheema Samriddhi\u201d or \u201cSheema Sukriti\u201d in my notes right now. What I do have is information on Kshema\u2019s crop insurance options, government schemes like PMFBY, weather-based plans, and customised seasonal covers. Would you like a summary of the available crop insurance plans, or should I arrange a callback\", \"message_id\": \"bd357411-fbc4-49bf-afbe-4568c3067494\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:29:19.919+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Okay. Are you providing any fire insurance\", \"message_id\": \"380926\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:29:41.817+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"plan?\", \"message_id\": \"381052\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:29:42.651+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"Yes, Kshema does provide fire insurance plans. The Kshema Shop Insurance Policy covers losses from fire for shops and commercial establishments. It protects your building, stock, equipment, and business contents against fire and other risks. Do you want to know the claim process or more about coverage?\", \"message_id\": \"fde03098-228e-411c-9056-440e1fafdef0\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:29:44.441+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Okay. But fine.\", \"message_id\": \"385859\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:30:05.313+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Is there any health insurance\", \"message_id\": \"385996\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:30:06.192+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"plans are there, like,\", \"message_id\": \"386238\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:30:07.755+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"my friend is, like, one leg is fractured.\", \"message_id\": \"387812\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:30:12.761+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Is there any plan suitable for\", \"message_id\": \"388258\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:30:14.637+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"my friend?\", \"message_id\": \"388445\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:30:15.433+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"Okay, for your friend with a fractured leg, Kshema offers the Individual Personal Accident Policy. This plan covers disabilities\", \"message_id\": \"59487103-925d-4e6d-a012-b31edee65bc7\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:30:17.978+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"Okay.\", \"message_id\": \"390827\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:30:24.928+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"Sorry, can you please repeat that? I couldn\u2019t hear you clearly.\", \"message_id\": \"9ecce669-2cce-423b-ac25-4444b676cc51\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:30:31.380+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"it's okay. You continue on\", \"message_id\": \"394346\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:30:39.644+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"personal accident\", \"message_id\": \"394886\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:30:41.591+00:00\"}, {\"user\": \"plan.\", \"message_id\": \"394987\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:30:42.009+00:00\"}, {\"bot\": \"Right, I\u2019ll continue. The Kshema Individual Personal Accident Policy covers loss of life and disabilities due to accidents. There are three plan options: Plan\", \"message_id\": \"5a10d248-792c-4f72-9097-7cf56bb83918\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-13T11:30:43.343+00:00\"}]",
